## Alp region hosts 50 karst springs from 4 countries:
01- Austria (44 karst springs)
02- France (1 karst spring)
03- Slovenia (4 karst springs)
04- Germany (1 karst spring)

Austrian data is provided by Simon Seelig, Jutta Eybl, and Gerfried Winkler. Original data source is "https://ehyd.gv.at". 
Austrian data is licensed by the original data brovider CC BY-NC 4.0. 

French data is provided by Bruno Arfib and Nathan Rispal. Original data source is the SNO Karst database "https://sokarst.org".

Slovenian data is provided by Natasa Ravbar and Cyril Mayaud. Original data source is "https://vode.arso.gov.si"

German data is downloaded from Bavarian Hydrometeorological Service "https://www.gkd.bayern.de/en/groundwater/flow-of-springs/tables"

For more information, please see Metadata table.
